BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:kpVQt7cuFBwGTjXgMVx5b
SUMMARY:Duo Comedy Improv Showcase
DTSTAMP:20260322T034727Z
DTSTART:20260326T030000Z
DESCRIPTION:Wednesdays from 8pm - 9:30pm Seattle’s only open mic for improv
	. Two-person improv teams! Double your pleasure\, double the fun. Seattle’
	s one and only open mic dedicated to two-person improv teams! Every week a
	t Unexpected Productions\, two-person teams take the stage to create hilar
	ious\, fast-paced\, totally unscripted comedy right before your eyes. No s
	cripts\, no safety nets—just pure improv magic. At Duos\, everyone shines.
	 Newer performers sharpen their game. Seasoned improvisers experiment\, ta
	ke risks\, and get wonderfully weird. The results? Quick-witted scenes\, s
	urprising twists\, and bold choices that feel impossible until you watch t
	hem happen live. Whether you dream of being the next Key & Peele\, Tina Fe
	y & Amy Poehler\, or a chaotic tag-team like Deadpool & Wolverine\, this i
	s your chance to take the mic and run with it. All experience levels are w
	elcome. Bring a friend\, form a team\, and give Seattle a show they won’t 
	forget. To sign up your duo\, email duoshowcase@gmail.com . Looki\n\nhttps
	://www.pikeplacemarket.org/events-calendar/duo-comedy-improv-showcase/?occ
	urrence=2026-03-25\n\nFrom Pike Place Market Events
URL:https://www.pikeplacemarket.org/events-calendar/duo-comedy-improv-showc
	ase/?occurrence=2026-03-25
LOCATION:Unexpected Productions\, 1428 Post Alley
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:events
CATEGORIES:Pike Place Market Events
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT1H30M
END:VEVENT
